&lt;h2&gt;A few things we're working on...&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Fluid workloads:&lt;/strong&gt; Getting bored with your server in Dallas? Soon you'll be able to automatically move to another location on Cloud.net.  
&lt;strong&gt;Improved account validation:&lt;/strong&gt; Providing an ID is annoying, for both of us. Just link your social media account, and you'll be automatically validated.  
&lt;strong&gt;Complete notification center:&lt;/strong&gt; Like to know everything going on with your account? With our notification center you'll know it all, and be notified through email or SMS.  
&lt;strong&gt;Numerous bug &amp; UI fixes:&lt;/strong&gt; The good news, a lot of these are done, just waiting on deployment. Others, such as rebuilding your server with the same OS &amp; specs are still being worked on. We'll keep you updated :)  

Want to help? You can submit your feature requests &amp; bug fixes at our &lt;a href="https://help.cloud.net/hc/en-us/community/topics/200026301-Feature-Requests"&gt;help center&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Free DNS hosting&lt;/h2&gt;

With any account, we offer completely free DNS hosting, using anycast DNS from 13 worldwide locations. See all the details at https://help.cloud.net/hc/en-us/sections/201359850-DNS

&lt;h2&gt;Full API&lt;/h2&gt;

Automate your deployment and management - we have a full API backend that allows you to create, and manage your servers using any tool you like. See the docs at https://api.cloud.net/docs.

&lt;h2&gt;One click app deployment&lt;/h2&gt;

Using our application deployment service to install more than 21 applications - see them all at https://help.cloud.net/hc/en-us/articles/207358950-What-applications-are-available-

&lt;h2&gt;The billing details...&lt;/h2&gt;

Don't look so glum - we've made it easy. $10 deposits are now available at Cloud.net.. We accept Paypal &amp; credit card - everything is PAYG, and we bill for a total of 672 total hours per month. If you cancel a server before the end of the month, you're credited back for the unused time. Here's what's hot - coupon codes apply to your entire account!
